(273, 1, 'ows_0499529', 'http://westandwiththe99percent.tumblr.com/post/11508628363', 'I''ve always had more than I need.\nIt''s not an...', NULL, NULL, '2011-10-16 10:00:42', NULL, NULL, 'I''ve always had more than I need. It''s not an accident or because of luck or because my family works harder than other people. We can only have so much more than we need when other people don''t have enough. I want a world where we all have what we need. I stand for reparations,...', 'http://westandwiththe99percent.tumblr.com/rss', NULL, 'We are the 1 percent', '', '2011-10-17 00:30:38'),
